General.Name: New Concept Energy Inc
General.Description: New Concept Energy, Inc. engages in real estate rental business. The company owns land located in Parkersburg, West Virginia. It provides advisory and management services for an independent oil and gas company. The company was formerly known as CabelTel International Corporation and changed its name to New Concept Energy, Inc. in May 2008. New Concept Energy, Inc. was founded in 1978 and is headquartered in Dallas, Texas.
